I dont know who it was that posted above that E'ci was the god of the Plane of Ice and Povar of the Plane of Vapor, but that is not the case.<br>
<br>
The Greater (Outer) Plane of Water is ruled by three gods, named the Triumverate of Water collectively.  These gods are Vapor, E'ci and Tarew Marr.  The rearranging of words is correct, but they all joinly rule the Elemental Plane of Water, and NOT of the sub parts.  Ie, there is no Plane of Vapor or Plane of Ice.<br>
